<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>레전드 음식 월드컵</title>
    <link href="/main.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
  </head>
  <body class="detail-main">
    <main>
      <div class="modal-bg">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <h1>참고이는 레전드 음식 월드컵</h1>
          <p>총 라운드를 선택하세요</p>
          <select
            class="form-select"
            aria-label="Round selection"
            id="roundSelection"
          >
            <option value="16">16강</option>
            <option value="32" selected>32강</option>
            <option value="64">64강</option>
          </select>
          <p>총 78명의 후보 중 무작위 32명이 대결합니다.</p>
          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" id="startGame">시작하기</button>
            <button class="btn btn-warning" id="viewRanking">랭킹보기</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <script>
      const startGameButton = document.getElementById("startGame");
      const viewRankingButton = document.getElementById("viewRanking");
      const roundSelection = document.getElementById("roundSelection");

      startGameButton.addEventListener("click", () => {
        const selectedRound = roundSelection.value;
        window.location.href = `/game/start?round=${selectedRound}`;
      });

      viewRankingButton.addEventListener("click", () => {
        window.location.href = "/game/ranking";
      });
    </script>

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
